# ============================================================================
# FightNight OS — Environment Variables (Expo / React Native)
# ============================================================================
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# NEVER commit .env to git — it contains secrets!
#
# NOTE: In Expo, client-side env vars use the EXPO_PUBLIC_ prefix
# (similar to NEXT_PUBLIC_ in Next.js or VITE_ in Vite).
# ============================================================================

